text: Tokkel tama Sagah cadok tut Rabe num Atuka Yalli kaa Aynuwweeleeh isi Qide num Siinih warse-lek keenik inne, tokkel too Sagah cadoytat kaa yootokeeniih Yalli kaa yuynuwweeh isi Qide num keenih warseh, Yalli tama num kah yuynuwwee innah Qhiyaamah Ayro Rabe mara yaynuwweh, israa-iil xayloy Yalli isi inkittinaanee kee isi dudda tascassee isi Astooti sin yaybulleeh cubbussaanaah tamahal kaskassoowa mara takkeenimkeh
